pr_title: PR: Implement Jakob and Hanika (2019) spectral upsampling
pr_body: An implementation of Jakob and Hanika (2019) spectral upsampling (#458). This is a part of my "New Spectral Upsampling Methods" GSoC 2020 project.

pr_title: PR: Implement CIE 2017 and ANSI/IES TM-30-18 Colour Fidelity Indexes.
pr_body:
The relevant issues are https://github.com/colour-science/colour/issues/408 and https://github.com/colour-science/colour/issues/207. This topic also appeared as a GSoC project idea: [New Colour Quality Metrics](https://github.com/colour-science/GSoC/blob/master/2020/GSoC-2020-Project-Ideas.md#new-colour-quality-metrics).

The two indexes are closely related, so I'll use the same branch and pull request for both. At the moment only the CIE index is implemented, the rest will follow in later commits.
